quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  24,37,"WorЙ“e Й“e soodugol e yeeyugol maapintaa Й—um gaayi jaЕ‹tagol Alla Senayee wonanii Mo, e tottirgol Julde nden no haaniri non, e jonnugol Jakka on henndotooЙ“e mo Й“en, hara hiЙ“e huli Г‘alnde Darngal, nden Г‘alaande nde waylitoytoo e muuЙ—um Й“erЙ—e Й—en hakkunde tama'u daЙ—ugol immorde e Lepte Й—en e kulol majje, giiЙ—e Й—en waylitoyoo e mayre faade e nokku kala ka Й—e yaari."
  24,38,"Ko Й“e golliri Й—um ko fii yo Alla yoЙ“u Й“e e dow golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude ko Й“e gollunoo kon, O Й“eydana Й“e kadi immorde e ЖЃural Makko ngal njoЙ“di e dow mu'un. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore e dow emmbere golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko woni hiMo okka Й“e cowe ko Й“e gollunoo kon."
  24,39,"ЖЃen yedduЙ“e Alla, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—e Й“e golli Й—en, Й—e maraa baraaji, ko yeru merere wonnde e hollaande Й—onЙ—aaЙ—o on no yi'a nde o sikka ko nde ndiyam, o yaha e mayre haa si o hewtii o daroo e hoore mayre o heЙ“ataa ndiyam, ko wano nii yedduЙ—o on himo sikka wonnde golle makko Й—en Й—e nafay mo, haa si o maayii o immintinaama hara o heЙ“atah baraaji golle Й—en. O tawa Joomi makko yeeso makko O huuЙ“inana mo hasboore golle makko Й—en haa timma, Alla ko O YaawuЙ—o Hasboore."
  24,40,"MaaЙ—um golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko yeru niЙ“e e nder maayo luggungo, no dow maggo benpeЖґЖґe, no dow Й—en benpeЖґЖґe benpeЖґЖґe goo, no dow majje duule hiЙ—e suddi koode tinddinorteeЙ—e Й—en, niЙ“e fawondirЙ—e yoga e majje e dow yoga, si ukkiiЙ—o e Й—ee niЙ“e Й—oo yaltinii junngo mu'un ngon o Й“adotaako yi'ugol ngo sabu saЙ—tude niЙ“e Й—en, ko wano nii kadi yedduЙ—o on, gomЙ—ii fawondirii e hoore makko niЙ“e majjere e sikke e wemmbere e uddeede Й“ernde makko, on mo Alla arsikaali Peewal immorde e majjere nden, e ganndal ka Deftere Makko, haray o marah peewal ngal o feewita Й—um, wanah kadi deftere nde o ndaygirta Й—um."
  24,41,"Kaa a anndaa -an NulaaЙ—o- wonndema Alla no subuhinanoo Mo Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli, no subuhinanoo Mo Й“en wonuЙ“e ka leydi immorde e tageefooji, colliЙ—in kadi no subuhinanoo Mo hiЙ—i fonti gabitanji(bibje) majji ka weeyo? Gootel kala e Й—ii tageefooji Alla hiMo Annadi Julde kala juuluЙ—o immorde e majji wano neЙ—Й—anke on, e subuhinaali kala subuhiniiЙ—o immorde e majji wano colli Й—in, Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e huuwata, suuЙ—anaaki Mo hay e huunde e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii kanko tun Laamu kammuuli Й—in e Laamu leydi ndin, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun woni ruttorde Г‘alnde Darngal fii Hasboore e njoЙ“di."
  24,43,"Kaa a anndaa -an NulaaЙ—o- wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira yoga e cenkoy mayre faade e yoga, refti O waЙ—a nde fawondirnde O dewta yoga e mayre e dow yoga, yi'aa toЙ“o ngon no yalta ka nder duulere, no iwa ka kammu jippoo immorde e Й—en duule sukkuЙ—e nannduЙ—e e pelle sabu mawnugol majje, [no yalta ton kadi] kunte ndiyam fenndiiЙ—am wa'uЙ—am wa koccuuje, O hewtina Й—en marmalle on mo O Muuyi immorde jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O firta Й—e e on mo O Muuyi e maЙ“Й“e, ndaygu maЖґe duule Й—en no do'a naЙ“ude giiЙ—e Й—en sabu saЙ—tude jalbugol majje."